%N A189868 Number of ways to place n nonattacking composite pieces queen + leaper[2,4] on an n X n chessboard.
%C A189868 a(n) is also number of permutations p of 1,2,...,n satisfying |p(i+2)-p(i)|<>4 AND |p(j+4)-p(j)|<>2 AND |p(m+k)-p(m)|<>k for all i>=1, j>=1, m>=1, k>=1, i+2<=n, j+4<=n, m+k<=n
